<refsect2 id="PolKitPolicyDefault" role="struct">
<title>PolKitPolicyDefault</title>
<indexterm zone="PolKitPolicyDefault"><primary>PolKitPolicyDefault</primary></indexterm><programlisting>typedef struct _PolKitPolicyDefault PolKitPolicyDefault;</programlisting>
<para>
Objects of this class are used to record information about a
default policy for an action.</para>
<para>

</para></refsect2>
